---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---
<SiteLayout title="Cynchorus — About" description="Overview of the Cynchorus project ethos, collaborators, and lab practices." ogImage="/favicon.svg">
  <section class="space-y-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-light uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-white sm:text-4xl">Project overview & ethos</h1>
    <p class="max-w-3xl text-lg text-slate-300">
      Cynchorus operates at the intersection of sonic research, systems engineering, and participatory design. We
      prototype living infrastructures that amplify resonance across human, machine, and ecological agents.
    </p>
    <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-8 backdrop-blur">
        <h2 class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-indigo-200">Lab Practice</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-300">
          Each experiment is conducted as an open score—documented, recorded, and shared with collaborators around the
          globe. Rituals prioritize embodied listening, consent-driven data stewardship, and public iteration logs.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-indigo-200/80">// TODO: content block — add lab principles & protocols</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-indigo-400/30 bg-indigo-400/10 p-8 backdrop-blur">
        <h2 class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-indigo-100">Collaborators</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-indigo-100/90">
          Core contributors include systems theorists, composers, software architects, and field researchers.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-indigo-200/70">// TODO: content block — list collaborators & partner nodes</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
